%2Fforum6.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6707896%26page%3D1&d=n56Gtz%2FeaVfJwK%2Fd5Uq8XI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0cbf0805\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6707896&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6728926&amp;type=BW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum6.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6728926%26type%3DBW&d=n56Gtz%2FeaVfJwK%2Fd5Uq8XI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=edc92834\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6728926&amp;type=BW</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUwants個邊既分析帖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=18785349&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.uwants.com%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D18785349%26extra%3Dpage%253D1%26page%3D1&d=n56Gtz%2FeaVfJwK%2Fd5Uq8XI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f0053d0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=18785349&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=1</a><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"401b7aa6224207f0b36e621151c2aae7d42fedf5","tid":279342,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">若果CD-ROM想加入群組的話<br />\n<br />\n可以自行去Uwants 開個新帳號<br />\n<br />\n之後再按照格式PM老夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(CD-ROM即是沒有高登帳號的人士) </div>"},{"pid":"29a4b42a7b4d4d870db92f25a72e5be0ec488039","tid":279342,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n金價現時正在打造雙頂回落<br />\n<br />\n(4月17日的高位1295.1及6月6日的高位1296.1形成雙頂)<br />\n<br />\n5月9日至6月6日此段期間     金價有可能正運行第五浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n若果運用黃金比率去計算的話<br />\n<br />\n0.5倍黃金比率剛好是1300心理關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n故金價在1296.1時掉頭回落也是合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n計法如下:<br />\n<br />\n第一至第三浪波幅: 1295.1-1122.6 = 172.5<br />\n<br />\n1213.7+172.5*0.5      = 1300    (心理關口)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以金價有可能借雙頂回落引起ABC下跌浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留意星期五出現大陰燭跌穿10天及20天WMA<br />\n<br />\n亦跌穿Keltner Channel 中軸及日本雲層圖轉勢線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n星期一可能會繼續下跌    <br />\n<br />\n但跌至基準線及Keltner Channel底線附近可能會暫停跌勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現階段來說<br />\n<br />\n星期一可以試試沽貨<br />\n<br />\n星期二至星期四則要隨機應變,相機行事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金價現正打造雙頂回落<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/2a7Cbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F2a7Cbc.jpg&h=124779e3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}